Package com.warzone.team08.CLI.models

Class CommandArgument

java.lang.Object
com.warzone.team08.CLI.models.CommandArgument
public class CommandArgument
extends java.lang.Object
Predefined structure for the command arguments and its value(s) It also provides the specification to: 1. Validate the number of values provided by the user 2. Validate each value with Regex
